TITLE: Setting Up the Main App with KeyboardAppView
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to configure the main app with the same keyboard configuration by wrapping the content view in a KeyboardAppView.
SOURCE: https://github.com/keyboardkit/keyboardkit/blob/master/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: swift
CODE:
```
@main
struct MyApp: App {

    var body: some Scene {
